message.entry: System must be a valid model or subsystem name.
Invalid NewBlock (<{0}>) passed to REPLACE_BLOCK. \nTry built-in/BLOCKTYPE or a valid block name.

The model must be unlocked to make changes to it. To unlock the model, select "Unlock Library" from the Diagram menu. Otherwise enter the command: \nset_param(bdroot(System),'Lock','off'), \nwhere System is the name of the system passed to replace_block.
